coordinates.MLFeatureShortDescription: Boxes × [x, y, width, height] (relative to image size)

iouThreshold.MLFeatureShortDescription: The maximum allowed overlap (as intersection-over-union ratio) for any pair of output bounding boxes (default: 0.45)

confidenceThreshold.MLFeatureShortDescription: The minimum confidence score for an output bounding box (default: 0.25)
